yer?']}, {'criterion': 'Overall Presentation and Detail', 'weight': 10, 'checklist': ['Is the response well-organized and easy to read?', 'Are the descriptions detailed enough to visualize the boss fights?', "Is there a logical flow to the presentation of each character's fight?", 'Are any additional elements (like environment or setting) mentioned?', 'Is the language clear and free of jargon?']}]}

